statements: SELECT * FROM WasteToEnergyData;
SELECT id, energy_output FROM WasteToEnergyData ORDER BY date DESC;
SELECT facility_name, energy_output FROM WasteToEnergyData WHERE energy_output > 1000;
SELECT date, facility_name FROM WasteToEnergyData ORDER BY facility_name ASC, date DESC;
SELECT CONCAT(facility_name, ' - Energy Output: ', energy_output) AS OutputInfo FROM WasteToEnergyData;
SELECT * FROM WasteToEnergyData WHERE energy_output > 5000 ORDER BY date DESC;
SELECT facility_name, SUM(energy_output) AS total_energy_output FROM WasteToEnergyData GROUP BY facility_name HAVING total_energy_output > 10000;
SELECT * FROM WasteToEnergyData WHERE facility_name LIKE 'A%' AND date >= '2022-01-01' ORDER BY energy_output DESC;
SELECT id, date, facility_name, energy_output FROM WasteToEnergyData WHERE date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-06-30' ORDER BY energy_output ASC;
SELECT facility_name, COUNT(id) AS total_records FROM WasteToEnergyData GROUP BY facility_name ORDER BY total_records DESC;
SELECT * FROM EnergyOutput;
SELECT id, date, energy_output_kwh FROM EnergyOutput WHERE location = 'New York';
SELECT location, energy_output_kwh FROM EnergyOutput ORDER BY energy_output_kwh DESC;
SELECT * FROM ProcessInfo WHERE process_id = 1;
SELECT process_name, process_description FROM ProcessInfo WHERE process_name LIKE '%optimization%';
SELECT * FROM EnergyOutput WHERE location = 'New York' ORDER BY date DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT location, SUM(energy_output_kwh) AS total_energy_output FROM EnergyOutput GROUP BY location ORDER BY total_energy_output DESC;
SELECT * FROM EnergyOutput JOIN ProcessInfo ON EnergyOutput.id = ProcessInfo.process_id WHERE process_name = 'Power Generation';
SELECT energy_output_kwh, process_name FROM EnergyOutput LEFT JOIN ProcessInfo ON EnergyOutput.id = ProcessInfo.process_id WHERE location = 'California';

SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_processes, AVG(energy_output_kwh) AS avg_energy_output FROM EnergyOutput JOIN ProcessInfo ON EnergyOutput.id = ProcessInfo.process_id GROUP BY location HAVING avg_energy_output > 5000;
SELECT * FROM WasteToEnergyProcesses;
SELECT process_id, process_date FROM WasteToEnergyProcesses ORDER BY process_date DESC;
SELECT process_id, energy_output FROM WasteToEnergyProcesses WHERE energy_output > 500;
SELECT * FROM EnergyOutputLogs WHERE log_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-03-31';
SELECT employee_name, employee_role FROM EnergyEmployees ORDER BY employee_name ASC;
SELECT process_id, process_date, energy_output FROM WasteToEnergyProcesses WHERE process_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT log_id, log_date, output_value FROM EnergyOutputLogs WHERE output_value > 1000 ORDER BY log_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM WasteToEnergyProcesses JOIN EnergyOutputLogs ON WasteToEnergyProcesses.process_id = EnergyOutputLogs.process_id;
SELECT employee_id, employee_name, employee_role FROM EnergyEmployees WHERE employee_role = 'Engineer';
SELECT process_id, SUM(output_value) AS total_output FROM EnergyOutputLogs GROUP BY process_id HAVING total_output > 5000;
SELECT * FROM Energy_Output;
SELECT id, energy_output FROM Energy_Output ORDER BY date DESC;
SELECT plant_name, location FROM Energy_Plants WHERE location = 'USA';
SELECT * FROM Waste_Storage WHERE waste_quantity > 100 ORDER BY waste_quantity DESC;

SELECT Energy_Plants.plant_name, Energy_Output.energy_output FROM Energy_Plants JOIN Plant_Energy_Output ON Energy_Plants.id = Plant_Energy_Output.plant_id JOIN Energy_Output ON Plant_Energy_Output.output_id = Energy_Output.id;
SELECT * FROM Energy_Output WHERE energy_output > 1000 ORDER BY date DESC
SELECT plant_name, location FROM Energy_Plants WHERE location LIKE 'New%'
SELECT output_id, plant_id FROM Plant_Energy_Output WHERE output_id IN (1,2,3) AND plant_id = 2
SELECT id, waste_quantity FROM Waste_Storage WHERE waste_type = 'Plastic' ORDER BY waste_quantity ASC
SELECT id, date, energy_output FROM Energy_Output WHERE date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2023-01-01'
SELECT * FROM EnergyOutput;
SELECT plant_name, location, capacity FROM PlantLocation WHERE capacity > 1000;
SELECT name, date, energy_output FROM EnergyOutput WHERE date >= '2022-01-01' ORDER BY energy_output DESC;
SELECT waste_type, percentage FROM WasteComposition WHERE percentage BETWEEN 10 AND 20;
SELECT plant_id, maintenance_date, cost FROM PlantMaintenance ORDER BY maintenance_date ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM EnergyOutput WHERE energy_output > 1000 ORDER BY date DESC;
SELECT plant_name, location, capacity FROM PlantLocation WHERE capacity > 500 ORDER BY plant_name;
SELECT waste_type, percentage FROM WasteComposition WHERE percentage >= 0.5 ORDER BY percentage DESC;
SELECT plant_id, maintenance_date, cost FROM PlantMaintenance WHERE cost < 5000 ORDER BY maintenance_date;
SELECT plant_id, consumption, reading_date FROM EnergyConsumption WHERE consumption < 1000 ORDER BY reading_date ASC;
